1
00:00:55,079 --> 00:00:55,840
Where's Xu Chi?

2
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:56,719
Uh...

3
00:00:56,719 --> 00:00:58,000
He went out to meet an author.

4
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:58,479
Oh.

5
00:00:58,479 --> 00:01:00,439
Another new author to sign a contract with?

6
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,759
Because Li Si's contract hasn't been finalized yet.

7
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:03,600
It's quite troublesome.

8
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:05,359
The boss is thinking of other ways to fix it.

9
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,719
The moon is so full tonight.

10
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:16,239
I remember when you just reached Ji grade,

11
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:19,040
we also encountered such a full moon.

12
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,599
It was when we just passed through Yuxia Pass.

13
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:24,480
We happened to be attacked by a pack of wolves.

14
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:27,680
You were the one who saved me from danger.

15
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:28,879
Then...

16
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,640
we collapsed by the creek, exhausted.

17
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:32,400
We looked up at the sky.

18
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:34,959
The moon that day was just as round.

19
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:38,159
I heard from Chaika about what happened with Li Si.

20
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,480
Why don't you

21
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:45,840
sign Li Si's novel with Xu Chi?

22
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,439
It would be a win-win for both of you.

23
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,280
Win-win?

24
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,120
And what about Li Si?

25
00:01:51,439 --> 00:01:52,400
What will happen to Li Si?

26
00:01:53,439 --> 00:01:54,439
Looks like you've forgotten

27
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,920
how I became Li Si in the first place.

28
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,000
Is this what you really think?

29
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:05,400
I don’t think Li Si’s situation is Xu Chi’s fault.

30
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,120
Everyone can make their own choices,

31
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:11,080
and they must take responsibility for their choices.

32
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,240
I was just saying that.

33
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:16,439
Let me think it over, okay?

34
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,159
Xu Chi's contract terms state

35
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,439
that I need to write five novels in three years.

36
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,400
You know,

37
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,400
I'm not Li Si after all.

38
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,479
It's quite hard for me.

39
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:31,199
I understand.

40
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,039
Honestly, I didn't want to ask this question,

41
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:38,479
but these past few days, seeing how you interact with Xu Chi,

42
00:02:38,479 --> 00:02:39,280
it's been on my mind.

43
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:42,479
Are you sure

44
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:45,000
what kind of feelings you have for him?

45
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,520
What do you mean?

46
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,680
Xu Chi is the one who created us.

47
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,719
He knows your personality, your temperament, and your hobbies

48
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:56,759
better than anyone else.

49
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,280
He wants you to like him,

50
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,199
depend on him,

51
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,199
even fall in love with him.

52
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:02,560
This is simply a piece of cake for him.

53
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:05,280
So, are you sure you really like him?

54
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,919
Besides, you two are from completely different worlds.

55
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,919
Everyone has their own path to walk.

56
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:14,639
Don’t tell me

57
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,800
you plan to stay here forever?

58
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,879
Xu Chi created me too,

59
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,680
and he knows me very well.

60
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,159
But between us,

61
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,240
there’s no such thing as one controlling the other.

62
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:31,199
We’re no longer just the author

63
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:33,560
and the character from his book.

64
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,360
It’s long since become more complicated than that.

65
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:37,400
If I find the way out of this world,

66
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,120
will you go back with me?

67
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:47,280
Although there are many things I find uncomfortable here,

68
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,599
I really like it here.

69
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,439
I want to be with Xu Chi.

70
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:56,879
Wherever he is,

71
00:03:58,039 --> 00:03:58,639
that’s where I’ll be.

72
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:15,360
Maybe I should let you know everything from the past.

73
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:23,680
Why hide it?

74
00:04:24,199 --> 00:04:25,360
Still keeping secrets from me?

75
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:26,439
Yes,

76
00:04:26,439 --> 00:04:27,360
I do have a secret.

77
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:28,160
Want to know?

78
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,120
I don’t really care.

79
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:31,040
I just came to tell you

80
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:31,759
Chai Ka has arrived.

81
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:32,680
The security won’t let him in.

82
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:34,199
I already told Xiao Chengjing to go pick him up.

83
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:36,120
Even on weekends, you’re making employees work.

84
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,199
Looks like you really don’t want to know, huh?

85
00:04:38,839 --> 00:04:39,519
How about this:

86
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,279
Let’s cancel the Qixi Festival date then.

87
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,600
A date?

88
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,639
What’s a date?

89
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:45,959
Give me a kiss, and I’ll tell you.

90
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,040
Boss

91
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,319
What is Li Si doing here?

92
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,720
I was startled when he came to pick me up earlier.

93
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,680
But he said he could sign it anytime.

94
00:05:04,199 --> 00:05:05,240
I just happen to have the agreement with me.

95
00:05:05,279 --> 00:05:06,079
Let’s have him sign it then.

96
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:12,519
How's the Qixi server update coming along?

97
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:13,399
Ah.

98
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,199
The acquisition process is fully completed.

99
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:16,800
All that’s left is for you to sign the agreement.

100
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:17,680
Tomorrow.

101
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,959
Our team will take over their tech department.

102
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:21,079
Tianya Haijiao (Edge of the World).

103
00:05:21,079 --> 00:05:23,439
This Qixi, server updates and maintenance will be discontinued.

104
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,560
The public announcements have been released online.

105
00:05:25,519 --> 00:05:25,879
Alright.

106
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:35,600
Maintenance happens once every three years.

107
00:05:36,519 --> 00:05:38,480
Xu Chi went to great lengths to acquire this website,

108
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:40,920
just to stop its Qixi maintenance.

109
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,399
Could this have something to do with our time-traveling?

110
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,399
The server updates—

111
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,800
could they be the exit to this world?

112
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:52,959
Yan Ying’s red string.

113
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:54,879
Xu Chi’s red string.

114
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,160
In the story, every three years,

115
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,480
Yan Ying disappears for a while.

116
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:00,680
And here, every three years,

117
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,160
the server gets updated once.

118
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,040
How could this be such a coincidence?

119
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,279
Why are you here?

120
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:38,079
What are you looking at?

121
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:51,120
Sparrow Wars.

122
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,360
Just browsing.

123
00:06:53,519 --> 00:06:54,600
If you like it,

124
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:55,319
you can go ahead and read it.

125
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:56,720
I’m leaving.

126
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:05,040
Xiao Chengjing actually likes reading this kind of book.
